rter.com/projects/chan-tze-woon/blue-island-a-film-on-hong-kong-protests?ref=9xjyk9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fchan-tze-woon%2Fblue-island-a-film-on-hong-kong-protests%3Fref%3D9xjyk9&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesba9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=b9eb81ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/chan-tze-woon/blue-island-a-film-on-hong-kong-protests?ref=9xjyk9</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>《亂世備忘》導演陳梓桓夥拍《十年》監製 拍反送中紀錄片 眾籌製作費<br />\n</ins></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「不是因為有自由的空間而做電影，而是電影創作是走向自由的方向。」</strong></span>《國安法》壓境之際，雨傘運動紀錄片《亂世備忘》導演陳梓桓說。他確信時代越艱難，越能做更自由的電影。如今經歷反送中運動，他將帶來新作《憂鬱之島》。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>《憂鬱之島》特別找來經歷過 2019 年與 2020 年抗爭的年輕人</strong></span>，重演三位主角在六十至八十年代的三段記憶﹕67 暴動、逃港潮、89 民運。陳梓桓在預告片中說：「反送中唔係一朝一夕嘅事，而係香港人一路走來的路」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%BA%82%E4%B8%96%E5%82%99%E5%BF%98-%E5%B0%8E%E6%BC%94%E9%99%B3%E6%A2%93%E6%A1%93%E5%A4%A5%E6%8B%8D-%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4-%E7%9B%A3%E8%A3%BD-%E6%8B%8D%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E7%89%87-%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C%E8%B2%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25BA%2582%25E4%25B8%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BF%2598-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A1%2593%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E6%258B%258D-%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A3%25BD-%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25B4%2580%25E9%258C%2584%25E7%2589%2587-%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25B2%25BB%2F&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesba9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=cc2349f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E4%25BA%2582%25E4%25B8%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BF%2598-%25E5%25B0%258E%25E6%25BC%2594%25E9%2599%25B3%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%25A1%2593%25E5%25A4%25A5%25E6%258B%258D-%